  "prompt": "What are the best restaurants to try when visiting Hubbali, Karnataka, India? What should you try while you're there?",
  "response": "Hubballi, located in Karnataka, India, is known for its rich culinary heritage. Here are some of the best restaurants to try when visiting, along with must-try dishes:\n\n### Best Restaurants in Hubballi\n\n1. **Hotel Gokul**\n   - **Cuisine:** South Indian, North Indian\n   - **Must-Try:** Masala Dosa, Idli Vada, and their famous South Indian Thali.\n   - **Why Visit:** Known for its authentic South Indian cuisine, this place offers a delicious and affordable dining experience.\n\n2. **The Nawaz Restaurant**\n   - **Cuisine:** Mughlai, North Indian\n   - **Must-Try:** Biryani, Butter Chicken, and various kebabs.\n   - **Why Visit:** A popular spot for non-vegetarian lovers, known for its rich flavors and hearty portions.\n\n3. **Trupthi Hotel**\n   - **Cuisine:** South Indian, North Indian\n   - **Must-Try:** Rava Idli, Vada Sambar, and their special Thali.\n   - **Why Visit:** A favorite among locals and tourists alike for its tasty and hygienic food.\n\n4. **Kamat Yatrinivas**\n   - **Cuisine:** South Indian, North Indian\n   - **Must-Try:** Filter Coffee, Dosa, and Puri Bhaji.\n   - **Why Visit:** A great place to enjoy traditional South Indian breakfast and other meals in a clean and comfortable environment.\n\n5. **Shri Renuka Darshini**\n   - **Cuisine:** South Indian\n   - **Must-Try:** Benne Dosa, Idli, and their variety of dosas.\n   - **Why Visit:** Famous for its delicious dosas and other South Indian snacks, offering a quick and satisfying meal.\n\n### Must-Try Dishes in Hubballi\n\n- **Masala Dosa**: A South Indian staple, this is a must-try for its crispy texture and spicy potato filling.\n- **Benne Dosa**: Similar to Masala Dosa but made with ghee, giving it a rich flavor.\n- **Rava Idli**: A variation of the traditional idli, made with semolina instead of rice, popular in Karnataka.\n- **Biryani**: Especially the one at The Nawaz Restaurant, known for its aromatic and flavorful preparation.\n- **Thali**: A complete meal that includes a variety of dishes, offering a taste of both South and North Indian cuisine.\n- **Filter Coffee**: A strong and aromatic coffee that\u2019s a staple in South Indian households and perfect to finish off your meal.\n\nWhen visiting Hubballi, make sure to explore these restaurants and try the recommended dishes to get a true taste of the local cuisine. Enjoy your culinary journey in this vibrant city!",
